@NODE "Non" "AmigaDOS For Beginners - Read Me First!! - Non Amigaguide Version"

@{B}@{U}@{JCENTER}AMIGADOS FOR BEGINNERS@{UU}

@{B}@{U}@{JCENTER}NON AMIGAGUIDE VERSION FOR WB 1.x@{UB}@{UU}
@{JLEFT}

I have a non Amigaguide version that uses a hypertext program called
"HT" which works reasonably well under Workbench 1.3 and earlier.

However, @{B}BE WARNED@{UB} that this is an early version of "AmigaDOS For Beginners"
and there may be omissions and inaccuracies in it. In particular, it does
@{B}NOT@{UB} take into account any changes in AmigaDOS from @{B}Version 3.0 onwards@{UB}.

I @{B}DO NOT@{UB} intend to waste time going through it looking for any such
omissions and inaccuracies. The demand for this version would be far too
small to warrant it.

If you order this version, I will NOT be held responsible for any such
omissions and inaccuracies.


