@NODE "ARB" "AmigaDOS For Beginners - ARexx For Beginners"

@{B}@{U}@{JCENTER}AMIGADOS FOR BEGINNERS

AREXX FOR BEGINNERS@{UB}@{UU}
@{JLEFT}

Written especially for beginners to the Amiga and/or @{"ARexx" LINK "ADB:Misc/Glossary/ARexx"} this set of
Amigaguide documents contains (approximately):-

   54 Articles
    3 Appendices
    1 Glossary
  228 Example ARexx scripts

Its aim is to lead the beginner through the intricacies of using ARexx.

Many of these articles have previously appeared in "Peripheral", the
magazine of @{"Commodore Hornsby User Group Inc." LINK "ADB:Misc/Glossary/CHUG"}, but have all been revised
and updated for inclusion in this set.

"ARexx For Beginners" is @{B}not@{UB} Public Domain. Demo versions are available
through my @{"web home page" LINK "ADB:Misc/Read_Me_First!!/Author"} or through Aminet (docs/help).


